headline: Mesa Labs (MLAB) Stock Jumps 5.7%: Will It Continue to Soar?
summary: Mesa Labs (MLAB) was a big mover last session on higher-than-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions might not help the stock continue moving higher in the near term.
